Former BBNaija housemate, Dorathy has admitted that she performed oral sex with Brighto while in the house. Dorathy said this on Tuesday night during BBNaija reunion show. Recall that Wathoni had earlier accused her of performing oral sex in the house. Confirming this, Dorathy told Ebuka that she had oral sex with Brighto because she liked him then. Dorathy said: “I gave Brighto a blow job, I admit with my full chest. “ After suck*ng Brighto’s dick he didn’t check on me the next day, he just walked past me and acted like nothing happened.”